    Stirling number of the third kind.
    Lah numbers.

    5! eq 定值 eq C(5,2)*2!*C(3,3)*3!
    C(6,1)*C(5,2)*C(3,3) eq 定值 eq C(6,2)*C(4,3)*C(1,1)
